Soccerama,pro,API,is,a,data,streaming,platform,for,professional,soccer,competitions,The,API,generates,full,season,analyses,for,leagues,tournaments,teams,players,and,all,fixtures,It,sends,requests,in,HTTP,protocol,and,returns,responses,in,JSON,format,The,API,s,provider,extends,coverage,to,over,leagues,and,cup,competitions,around,the,world,However,the,number,of,leagues,accessible,by,the,API,depends,on,specific,standard,or,customized,plans,priced,at,between,EUR,and,EUR